    <item>
      <title>Indian Winter</title>
      <link>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/indian-winter/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2018 11:54:50 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/indian-winter/</guid>
      <description>
&lt;div class=&#34;recipe-intro p-summary&#34;&gt;This uses &lt;a href=&#34;https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/ingredients/simple-syrup/#honey-syrup&#34;&gt;honey syrup&lt;/a&gt; infused with cardomom pods.&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;ul class=&#34;ingredients&#34;&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;1½ oz vodka&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;½ oz lemon juice&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;½ oz honey cardamom syrup&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;1 egg white&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;2 drops Angostura bitters&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;1 star anise&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;div class=&#34;instructions e-instructions&#34;&gt;
  Add vodka, lemon juice, syrup, and egg white to a shaker. &lt;a href=&#34;https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/techniques/shaking/#dry-shaking&#34;&gt;Dry shake&lt;/a&gt;, then add ice and shake. &lt;a href=&#34;https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/techniques/straining/#double-straining&#34;&gt;Double-strain&lt;/a&gt; into a coupe glass.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Add a couple drops of Angostura bitters on top of the foam (for aroma). Float the star anise atop the drink.
&lt;/div&gt;


